{"lemma":"مُحَمَّلِي","slug":"مُحَمَّلِي","root":"ح.م.ل","root_slug":"ح-م-ل","root_link":"/words/roots/ح-م-ل","pos":"N","pos_camel":"noun","paradigm":[],"frequency_in_corpus":0,"cross_references":{"qac":{"found":false},"wiktextract":{"found":false},"lanes":{"found":true,"entry_ids":["n9189","n9190","n9191","n44361"],"search_url":"https://lanelexicon.com/?s=%D9%85%D9%8F%D8%AD%D9%8E%D9%85%D9%8E%D9%91%D9%84%D9%90%D9%8A"}},"translations":null,"definition":null,"etymology":null,"ipa":null,"lanes_definition":{"source":"lanes","entries":[{"entry_id":"n9189","headword_ar":"مَحْمِلٌ","root":"Hml","body":[{"kind":"text","text":"[of which the primary signification is"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A place of bearing"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"carrying"},{"kind":"text","text":"], (S, Mgh, Msb, K,) or ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"miHomalN","text_ar":"مِحْمَلٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"[which primarily signifies"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"An instrument for bearing"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"carrying"},{"kind":"text","text":"], (M, Mgh,) or the latter is allowable, (Msb,) The ["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"kind of vehicle called"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"hawodaj","text_ar":"هَوْدَج"},{"kind":"text","text":"; (Msb;) as also ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"HimolN","text_ar":"حِمْلٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":": (M, K:) or the"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"large"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"hwdj","text_ar":"هودج"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"termed"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Haj~aAjiY~N","text_ar":"حَجَّاجِىٌّ"},{"kind":"text","text":": (Mgh:) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a pair of dorsers,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"panniers,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"oblong chests,"},{"kind":"text","text":"("},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"$iq~aAni","text_ar":"شِقَّانِ"},{"kind":"text","text":",)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"upon a camel, in which are borne two equal loads,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(K,) ["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"and which, with a small tent over them, compose a"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"hwdj","text_ar":"هودج"},{"kind":"text","text":";]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"first made use of by El-Hajjáj Ibn-Yoosuf Eth-Thakafee:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"one of the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"maHaAmil","text_ar":"مَحَامِل"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"of the pilgrims:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S:)"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"maHaAmilu","text_ar":"مَحَامِلُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"being the pl. (K.) Hence, ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"maHaAmiliY~N","text_ar":"مَحَامِلِىٌّ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A seller of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"maHaAmil","text_ar":"مَحَامِل"},{"kind":"text","text":". (K.) [What is now particularly termed the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"mHml","text_ar":"محمل"},{"kind":"text","text":"(vulgarly pronounced"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"maHomal","text_ar":"مَحْمَل"},{"kind":"text","text":") of the pilgrims is an ornamented"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"hwdj","text_ar":"هودج"},{"kind":"text","text":", which is borne by a camel, but without a rider, and is regarded as the royal banner of the caravan; such as is described and figured in my work on the Modern Egyptians. (See also"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"maHaArapN","text_ar":"مَحَارَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", in art."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Hwr","text_ar":"حور"},{"kind":"text","text":".)] Its application to (tropical:)  The"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"camel that bears the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"mHml","text_ar":"محمل"},{"kind":"text","text":"is tropical. (Mgh.) [See also"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"HimolN","text_ar":"حِمْلٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":". The assertion that it signifies also the silk covering that is sent every year for the Kaabeh is erroneous. This covering is sent from Cairo, with the baggage of the chief of the Egyptian pilgrim-caravan.] ―         -b2-  Also"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"maHomilN","text_ar":"مَحْمِلٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (K,) or ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"miHomalN","text_ar":"مِحْمَلٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", (M,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A basket"},{"kind":"text","text":"("},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"zinobiyl","text_ar":"زِنْبِيل"},{"kind":"text","text":")"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"in which grapes are carried to the place where they are to be dried;"},{"kind":"text","text":"and so ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"HaAmilapN","text_ar":"حَامِلَةٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":". (K.) ―         -b3-  One says also,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"maA EalaY fulaAnK maHomilN","text_ar":"مَا عَلَى فُلَانٍ مَحْمِلٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(assumed tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"There is no ground of reliance upon such a one;"},{"kind":"text","text":"syn."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"muEotamadN","text_ar":"مُعْتَمَدٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":": (S:) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"no relying,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"reliance:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(MA:) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"no ground"},{"kind":"text","text":"(lit."},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"place"},{"kind":"text","text":")"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"for imposing upon such a one the accomplishment of one's wants."},{"kind":"text","text":"(M, TA.) And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"maA EalaY AlbaEiyri maHomilN mino viqali AlHimoli","text_ar":"مَا عَلَى البَعِيرِ مَحْمِلٌ مِنْ ثِقَلِ الحِمْلِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(assumed tropical:)  ["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"There is no ground of reliance,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"no relying, upon the camel, by reason of the heaviness of the load."},{"kind":"text","text":"] (TA.)"}],"source_refs":["S","Mgh","Msb","K","M","TA","MA"]},{"entry_id":"n9190","headword_ar":"مُحْمِلٌ","root":"Hml","body":[{"kind":"text","text":"A woman, (S, M, K,) and a she-camel, (S, M,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"who yields her milk without being pregnant."},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, M, K.)"}],"source_refs":["S","M","K"]},{"entry_id":"n9191","headword_ar":"مِحْمَلٌ","root":"Hml","body":[{"kind":"text","text":": see"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"maHomilN","text_ar":"مَحْمِلٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", in two places. ―         -b2-  The"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"EilaAqap","text_ar":"عِلَاقَة"},{"kind":"text","text":"of a sword (S, Msb, * K) &c.; (Msb;) i. e. its"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"suspensory thong"},{"kind":"text","text":"[or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"cord"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"shoulder-belt"},{"kind":"text","text":"],"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"by which the wearer hangs it upon his neck;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, TA;) as also ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"HimaAlapN","text_ar":"حِمَالَةٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, Msb, K) and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"HamiylapN","text_ar":"حَمِيلَةٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":": (IDrd, K:) and the ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"HimaAlap","text_ar":"حِمَالَة","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"of the bow is similar to that of the sword: the wearer throws it upon his right shoulder, and puts forth his left arm from it, so that the bow is on his back: (AHn, TA:) the pl. of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"miHomalN","text_ar":"مِحْمَلٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"is"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"maHaAmilu","text_ar":"مَحَامِلُ"},{"kind":"text","text":": (Az, Msb:) and that of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"HimaAlapN","text_ar":"حِمَالَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (S, Msb,) or of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"HamiylapN","text_ar":"حَمِيلَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (Kh, TA,) is ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"HamaAy^ilu","text_ar":"حَمَايِلُ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"; (Kh, S, TA;) or, accord. to As,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"HamaAy^ilu","text_ar":"حَمَايِلُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"has no proper sing., its sing. being only"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"miHomalN","text_ar":"مِحْمَلٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":". (S, TA.) ―         -b3-  Dhu-r-Rummeh applies it to (tropical:)  The"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"root of a tree;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, K;) likening this to the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"mHml","text_ar":"محمل"},{"kind":"text","text":"of a sword. (S.) ―         -b4-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"maHaAmilu Al*~akari","text_ar":"مَحَامِلُ الذَّكَرِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"HamaAy^iluhu","text_ar":"حَمَايِلُهُ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"(assumed tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"The veins in the root and skin of the penis."},{"kind":"text","text":"(M, K.)"}],"source_refs":["S","Msb","K","IDrd","AHn","TA","Az","Kh"]},{"entry_id":"n44361","headword_ar":"مُحْمَلٌ","root":"hml","body":[{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Having no government."},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA, art. on the particle"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"fa","text_ar":"فَ"},{"kind":"text","text":".) ―         -b2-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"lafoZN muHomalN","text_ar":"لَفْظٌ مُحْمَلٌ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A word that has no grammatical government; contr. of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"EaAmilN","text_ar":"عَامِلٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":". (IbrD.)"}],"source_refs":[]}]},"classical_definitions":null}